    • Method Detail

      • refreshVisuals

        public void refreshVisuals()
        The refreshVisuals of this EditPart(all shape editparts) updates the text(shorten shape name), the boundaries and the tooltip(complete shape name) of the Shape figure. The refreshVisuals of this EditPart the names of all groups and compartmenttype in the child Model are added to the compartmentPart and the method ORMSuperShapeEditPart.refreshVisuals() is called.

        refreshVisuals in class ORMSuperShapeEditPart
